description:
A Brother and Sister leave our world and its rules behind, journeying into legend through the Butterfly Gate, where every step they take will come at a price.

Butterfly Gate follows the story of two siblings who, after throwing themselves headlong into another world, must face the brutal reality that lies beyond and find their place amidst an empire built after a revolution against the Gods.

An ongoing, episodic, SF odyssey, Butterfly Gate is also a silent comic, conveying the story purely through its imagery.

EISBN: 978-1-4733-6535-3
Days on Dalduin is a colorful, science fiction adventure novel. There is no tekst. Some of the story telling is done with illustrated balloons.

Sink or Swim

Nessie races to save Leon's life. Cthulhu regains his powers. Noah triumphantly returns to his ark. An old nemesis returns. Enemies are vanquished and friends reunited! All this and more in the thrilling conclusion to the first volume of Noah's Brother's Ark!
name: Sink or Swim

description:
It all begins here. Do not skip to the last page. Do not let a friend or message board ruin this comic for you. The future (and past) of the DC Universe starts here. Don’t say we didn’t warn you!
